Package eu.stratosphere.nephele.rpc

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RPCProtocol
    Base interface every RPC protocol must inherit.
    RPCTestProtocol
    This interface represents a test protocol used as part of the RPC unit tests.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CommonTypeUtils
    This utility class provides a list of types frequently used by the RPC protocols included in this package.
    MultiPacketOutputStreamTest
    This class contains unit tests for the MultiPacketOutputStream.
    RPCEnvelope
    An RPC envelope is the basic data structure which wraps all other types of messages for the RPC communication.
    RPCMessage
    Abstract base class for all types of communication messages used by this RPC service.
    RPCService
    This class implements a lightweight, UDP-based RPC service.
    RPCServiceTest  
    RPCStatistics
    The RPCStatistics class collects statistics on the operation of the RPC service, e.g. packet loss, request retries, etc.
